00:10:50,708 --> 00:10:51,916
[NADJA] What happened next?

224
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,416
After that... the shop
owner put up quite a fight.

225
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:56,041
But he was no
match for all three

226
00:10:56,125 --> 00:10:58,000
and received
near-fatal injuries.

227
00:10:58,083 --> 00:11:00,041
[DOG COP] This is
where he went down.

228
00:11:00,125 --> 00:11:01,916
[DOG COP] That poor man
never would have suffered

229
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,833
if you folks from the
World Salvation Committee

230
00:11:03,916 --> 00:11:05,541
could keep tabs on your perps.

231
00:11:05,625 --> 00:11:07,000
Shut your face or I'll...

232
00:11:08,333 --> 00:11:10,750
Uh... Are you
two doin' okay?

233
00:11:10,833 --> 00:11:12,750
We'll be fine once we
apprehend these criminals,

234
00:11:12,833 --> 00:11:14,000
so it's pertinent
that you give us

235
00:11:14,083 --> 00:11:16,000
all the information you have.

236
00:11:16,083 --> 00:11:19,750
[NADJA] So officer...
what leads can you... pass on?

237
00:11:19,833 --> 00:11:22,291
Well... a report came through
that placed your burglars

238
00:11:22,375 --> 00:11:25,000
hitting more antique stores
in the next town over.

239
00:11:25,083 --> 00:11:27,458
[BOTH] Next town... over?

240
00:11:27,541 --> 00:11:29,208
[DOG COP] Yeah. Once
you make it over those two

241
00:11:29,291 --> 00:11:31,500
mountain peaks it's
right on the other side.

242
00:11:31,583 --> 00:11:32,958
[BOTH groan]

243
00:11:33,041 --> 00:11:35,083
[DOG COP] It should
only take a day or two.

244
00:11:35,166 --> 00:11:37,458
[BOTH sigh]

